---
title: Tex-Mex Beef & Bell Pepper Grain Bowls 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: Got one pan and 20 minutes to spare? That’s all you need to get this filling, flavorful Mexican-style bowl on the table in a snap. You'll sauté bell pepper and ground beef with Mexican spices and our bold Tex-Mex paste. Then, you’ll pile it atop a quick cooking whole grain blend and dollop with tangy sour cream, guacamole, and crunchy tortilla chips.
